{"tid":516592,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"asso博上u係回收社會垃圾既最佳方法","createTime":"2018-01-01T14:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T14:32:31.000Z","uid":100391,"like":41,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c6efa9f0a9cbed5da7ef8ea82882314fee456430","tid":516592,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"見咁多人屌後門狗所以想認真討論下<br />\n<br />\n首先，政府推asso係因為d人成日瓜瓜嘈 話唔夠學士學位blablabla<br />\n但係政府要開多1個ugc學位係要比好多錢<br />\nd學生jupas都冇offer 姐係個人好蠢 洗咁多錢比佢地計續讀咪好唔抵<br />\n所以就推出一個垃圾回收計畫asso 揀啲有心讀書既垃圾出黎<br />\nsenior entry既ugc學位讀少1、2年 所以對政府黎講會平好多<br />\n加上出面d hr知咩事 會screen走asso 讀起果班 <br />\n<br />\n所以其實人地走後門係益左班真大學生<br />\n如果政府加開ugc instead of asso，咁班垃圾咪同你平起平坐做正大學生囉"},{"pid":"7cb6308ae7b2f559b6df87c1babd6d22b2705876","tid":516592,"uid":150611,"like":15,"dislike":18,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e73410e71025ccd5467a1e9f9fc5d234eb124397","tid":516592,"uid":91813,"like":32,"dislike":6,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"cv只寫ugc咪得 screen乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f042b6816ea0ce2e1733f4efe02c491eb714503c","tid":516592,"uid":138923,"like":39,"dislike":5,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"e73410e71025ccd5467a1e9f9fc5d234eb124397","tid":516592,"uid":91813,"like":32,"dislike":6,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"cv只寫ugc咪得 screen乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"中六過渡到大學中間消失左2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上2年就大學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知發生左咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ef7f18f40bdd5f03bdb72df8c6a2e6bd19a35e","tid":516592,"uid":78392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f5133fbcd2a67b354300cc